1. **SPEC.md** - The evolving vision (versioned when it changes) - the ideal final state
2. **CURRENT.md** - Active project state and features
3. **DELTA.md** - Work in progress (merge to SPEC/CURRENT regularly)

NEVER CREATE: GUIDE_v2_FINAL.md, TODO.md, NOTES.md, feature-specific.md files
ALWAYS: Archive old docs, consolidate scattered docs, keep README minimal
</documentation_organization>

